summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 234E, page 31, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in East 140' of South 1/2 of Tract 3, Earl J. McLaughlins Addition located on Northwest corner 35th Ave. N.E. and East 87th St. as Multiple Residence (RM) Zone.
